<DOC><DOCNO> DOE2-26-0058 </DOCNO><TEXT>Messrs. Hi-Reach International Ltd. have developed an inspection and servicingplatform for vertical bunkers. The steel platform is suspended in fourpoints; it is raised and lowered by four hydraulic Tirak continuous hoists,type THB 1000 MS, each with a useful power of 1000 daN. The hoistingcables run on deflection pulleys mounted on the platform and are fastenedto the bunker roof. A maximum speed of 3.5 m/min was found to be mostfavourable for the work to be done. Cables with a diameter of 9.5 mmand a rupture strength of 6400 daN are used. The design and performanceof the system are gone into. (MOS).</TEXT></DOC>